204
00:09:38,010 --> 00:09:41,514
I had a blast myself
talking about the good old days.

205
00:09:45,818 --> 00:09:47,253
Did it make you want to return?

206
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,454
To Showa?

207
00:09:51,457 --> 00:09:52,825
I can't.

208
00:09:53,326 --> 00:09:54,961
I'm too busy, thanks to you guys.

209
00:09:55,561 --> 00:09:56,896
I'm going to be on TV.

210
00:09:57,663 --> 00:09:58,698
What?

211
00:09:59,231 --> 00:10:01,701
Wait, you two know each other?

212
00:10:01,767 --> 00:10:03,235
That'll save us time.

213
00:10:03,302 --> 00:10:05,871
I was just looking for a participant.

214
00:10:06,372 --> 00:10:09,208
Mr. Kazushige Nagashima
keeps going away to Hawaii.

215
00:10:11,010 --> 00:10:12,044
