220
00:10:20,152 --> 00:10:21,554
TV is so dull these days.

221
00:10:22,121 --> 00:10:24,156
Everyone's so neutral.

222
00:10:24,223 --> 00:10:25,291
Don't you agree, Uryu?

223
00:10:25,791 --> 00:10:26,626
You

224
00:10:27,159 --> 00:10:28,160
should be on this.

225
00:10:28,227 --> 00:10:30,196
So, I'll be staying here for a while.

