00:12:12,732 --> 00:12:14,834
What is this place? What university?

244
00:12:14,900 --> 00:12:17,369
The lab of the Metropolis Institute
of Technology.

245
00:12:17,436 --> 00:12:19,371
Please go see Junko.

246
00:12:20,439 --> 00:12:21,273
What?

247
00:12:22,908 --> 00:12:23,776
Um…

